description: This file contains internal definitions, function prototypes, and ASN.1 object structure description related to RSADigestInfo, used in ASN.1 encoding/decoding for cryptographic functions within a C project.

methods.name: AnscAsn1RSADigestInfoCreateChildAttr
methods.description: Creates and returns the attributes for a child object of ASN.1 RSADigestInfo at a specified index.

methods.name: AnscAsn1RSADigestInfoGetChildName
methods.description: Returns the name of a child object of ASN.1 RSADigestInfo at a specified index.

methods.name: AnscAsn1RSADigestInfoCreateChildObject
methods.description: Creates and returns a child ASN.1 object based on the given index.
